---

---

<section class="bg-surface py-16 px-6 md:px-24">
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-24 gap-8 fade-up">
    <div class="max-w-xl">
      <h2
        class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter text-zinc-900 mb-6 uppercase"
        data-i18n="process.header"
      >
        Refining the<br />Rental Ethos.
      </h2>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-primary mb-6"></div>
    </div>
    <p
      class="max-w-xs text-zinc-500 font-label text-xs uppercase tracking-widest leading-loose"
      data-i18n="process.desc"
    >
      We have dismantled the traditional rental process, replacing it with a
      curated concierge-led flow designed for the modern professional.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-0 border-t border-zinc-100">
    <!-- Step 1 -->
    <div
      class="group relative pt-12 pl-6 pr-12 md:px-12 pb-24 md:border-r border-zinc-100 hover:bg-white transition-colors duration-500 fade-up"
    >
      <span
        class="block text-primary font-extrabold text-7xl mb-12 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
        >01</span
      >
      <h3
        class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight"
        data-i18n="step1.title"
      >
        Select Vehicle
      </h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed mb-8 font-body" data-i18n="step1.desc">
        Browse our curated autodrome of premium electric and hybrid models. From the performance-tier Tesla to rugged Jeep profiles, find your ideal match.
      </p>
      <a href="/fleet"
        class="flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest cursor-pointer"
      >
        <span data-i18n="process.explore">Explore Collection</span>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Step 2 -->
    <div
      class="group relative pt-12 md:px-12 pb-24 md:border-r border-zinc-100 hover:bg-white transition-colors duration-500 fade-up"
    >
      <span
        class="block text-primary font-extrabold text-7xl mb-12 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
        >02</span
      >
      <h3
        class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight"
        data-i18n="step2.title"
      >
        Verify Protocol
      </h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed mb-8 font-body" data-i18n="step2.desc">
        Once your choice is locked, our concierge coordinates the identification and protocol verification. No paperwork—just a refined, tailored experience.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact"
        class="flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest cursor-pointer"
      >
        <span data-i18n="process.requirements">View Requirements</span>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Step 3 -->
    <div
      class="group relative pt-12 md:pl-12 pb-24 hover:bg-white transition-colors duration-500 fade-up"
    >
      <span
        class="block text-primary font-extrabold text-7xl mb-12 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
        >03</span
      >
      <h3
        class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight"
        data-i18n="step3.title"
      >
        Collective Motion
      </h3>
      <p class="text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed mb-8 font-body" data-i18n="step3.desc">
        Experience the new standard of motion. Your vehicle is delivered in pristine condition at your Paris location, ready for the French journey ahead.
      </p>
      <a href="/fleet"
        class="flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest cursor-pointer"
      >
        <span data-i18n="process.secure">Secure Allocation</span>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
